              Nice workstand - I like Ultimate's stuff - I have one of their cheaper stands.  <BR><BR>The Trek 520 is a classic - not cutting edge, but just good, solid engineering.  It's a sweet bike to have in the stable - very versatile and it will last you forever.<BR><BR>Edit - a bike stand is not a ride - that's what I get for typing while distracted

              

              
              
